<td><a href="http://www.icd9data.com/getICD9Code.ashx?icd9=296.80" class="external text" title="http://www.icd9data.com/getICD9Code.ashx?icd9=296.80" rel="nofollow">296.80</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th><a href="/wiki/OMIM" title="OMIM" class="mw-redirect">OMIM</a></th>
<td><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/dispomim.cgi?id=125480" class="external text" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/dispomim.cgi?id=125480" rel="nofollow">125480</a> <a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/dispomim.cgi?id=309200" class="external text" title="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/dispomim.cgi?id=309200" rel="nofollow">309200</a></td>
